_sText: Spawns 64. 4 buyzones. 4 spawns. The top level of this map includes 4 spawns, 2 ct, 2 t. When you spawn, both spawns next to you are enemy spawns. There is also a mini castle in the middle to get high advantage and cover. The second level consists of many glass barriers to stay behind to take less damage. The bottom level has 4 ramps to surf on to jump to one of the small glass platforms or the ladder that will take you up to the 2nd level.
